data.description: This exquisite residence, nestled in the Brentwood subdivision, presents a meticulously renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch home. The kitchen is a focal point of beauty with its new flooring, soft close cabinets, quartz countertops, and state-of-the-art appliances. The bathrooms have undergone a stunning transformation, boasting new flooring, vanities, toilets, and elegantly tiled showers. The entire interior of the home and garage has been freshly painted, enhancing its overall allure. New roof installed in 2019, a sizeable backyard with a new 6-foot privacy fence, convenient shed and open canvas waiting for your imagination. Offering move-in readiness and a prime location, this property stands out as a must-see!
